@startuml
title 範本方法模式 (Template Method Pattern) - 咖啡因飲料系統

' --- 樣式設定 ---
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

skinparam class {
BackgroundColor White
ArrowColor #16a085
BorderColor #1abc9c
}

' ==========================================
' 1. 標準範本方法 (Standard Template)
' ==========================================
package "標準範本方法" {
abstract class CaffeineBeverage {
+ prepareRecipe(): void <<final>>
+ {abstract} brew(): void
+ {abstract} addCondiments(): void
+ boilWater(): void
+ pourInCup(): void
}

class Coffee extends CaffeineBeverage {
    + brew(): void
    + addCondiments(): void
}

class Tea extends CaffeineBeverage {
    + brew(): void
    + addCondiments(): void
}


}

' ==========================================
' 2. 帶有鉤子的範本方法 (Template with Hook)
' ==========================================
package "進階範本方法 (Hook)" {
abstract class CaffeineBeverageWithHook {
+ prepareRecipe(): void <<final>>
+ {abstract} brew(): void
+ {abstract} addCondiments(): void
+ boilWater(): void
+ pourInCup(): void
+ customerWantsCondiments(): boolean <<hook>>
}

class CoffeeWithHook extends CaffeineBeverageWithHook {
    + brew(): void
    + addCondiments(): void
    + customerWantsCondiments(): boolean
}

class TeaWithHook extends CaffeineBeverageWithHook {
    + brew(): void
    + addCondiments(): void
    + customerWantsCondiments(): boolean
}


}

' --- 說明註解 ---
note right of CaffeineBeverage::prepareRecipe
範本方法：定義了演算法的步驟：
1. boilWater()
2. brew()
3. pourInCup()
4. addCondiments() end note

note bottom of CaffeineBeverageWithHook
鉤子 (Hook)：
子類別可以選擇性覆寫
customerWantsCondiments()
來控制範本方法中的邏輯流。
end note

@enduml